long.am,ar,bn,ca,da,en,en_AU,en_GB,en_US,es_4: Allows Cloud Print and Scan users to print from the Chrome print screen to the Cloud Print and Scan web application.
long.bg: Позволява на потребителите на услугата Cloud Print and Scan да отпечатват от екрана за печат в Chrome към уеб приложението Cloud Print and Scan.
long.cs: Umožňuje uživatelům služby Cloud Print and Scan tisknout z tiskové obrazovky Chrome do webové aplikace Cloud Print and Scan.
long.de: Erlaubt Benutzern von Cloud Print and Scan über das Druckfenster von Chrome in die Webanwendung von Cloud Print and Scan zu drucken.
long.el: Επιτρέπει στους χρήστες του Cloud Print and Scan να εκτυπώνουν από την οθόνη εκτύπωσης του Chrome στη διαδικτυακή εφαρμογή Cloud Print and Scan.
long.es: Permite a los usuarios de Cloud Print and Scan imprimir desde la pantalla de impresión de Chrome en la aplicación web Cloud Print and Scan.
long.fr: Autorise les utilisateurs de Cloud Print and Scan à imprimer à partir de l'écran d'impression de Chrome vers l'application web Cloud Print and Scan.
long.he: מאפשר למשתמשי Cloud Print and Scan להדפיס ממסך ההדפסה של Chrome לאפליקציית האינטרנטית של Cloud Print and Scan.
long.hu: Lehetővé teszi a Cloud Print and Scan felhasználók számára, hogy a Chrome nyomtatási képernyőjéről a Cloud Print and Scan webes alkalmazásba nyomtassanak.
long.it: Consente agli utenti di Cloud Print and Scan di stampare dalla schermata di stampa di Chrome nell'applicazione web Cloud Print and Scan.
long.ja: Cloud Print and Scan ユーザーが Chrome の印刷画面から Cloud Print and Scan ウェブアプリケーションに印刷できるよう許可します。
long.ko: Cloud Print and Scan 사용자가 Chrome 화면 인쇄에서 Cloud Print and Scan 웹 애플리케이션으로 인쇄할 수 있도록 허용합니다.
long.lt: Leidžia "Cloud Print and Scan" naudotojams spausdinti iš "Chrome" spausdinimo ekrano į "Cloud Print and Scan" žiniatinklio programą.
long.nl: Staat toe aan gebruikers van Cloud Print and Scan om af te drukken vanaf het Chrome-afdrukscherm naar de webapplicatie Cloud Print and Scan.
long.pl,sl: Umożliwia użytkownikom Cloud Print and Scan drukowanie z ekranu drukowania Chrome do aplikacji internetowej Cloud Print and Scan.
long.pt_BR: Permite que os usuários do Cloud Print and Scan imprimam da tela de impressão do Chrome no aplicativo web Cloud Print and Scan.
long.ro: Permite utilizatorilor Cloud Print and Scan să imprime din ecranul de imprimare Chrome în aplicația web Cloud Print and Scan.
long.th: อนุญาตให้ผู้ใช้ Cloud Print and Scan พิมพ์จากหน้าจอการพิมพ์ของ Chrome ไปยังเว็บแอปพลิเคชัน Cloud Print and Scan
long.tr: Cloud Print and Scan kullanıcılarının Chrome yazdırma ekranından Cloud Print and Scan web uygulaması üzerinden yazdırmasına olanak tanır.
long.vi: Cho phép người dùng Cloud Print and Scan in từ màn hình in Chrome sang ứng dụng web Cloud Print and Scan.
long.zh_TW: 允許 Cloud Print and Scan 使用者從 Chrome 列印畫面列印至 Cloud Print and Scan 網頁應用程式。
